<p>Reverse an array of integers.  </p>

<p><strong>Function Description</strong>  </p>

<p>Complete the function <em>reverseArray</em> in the editor below.  </p>

<p><em>reverseArray</em> has the following parameter(s):  </p>

<ul>
<li><em>int A[n]</em>: the array to reverse  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Returns</strong>  </p>

<ul>
<li><em>int[n]</em>: the reversed array</li>
